Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊  雛菊小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  快點穿上些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  小颯  怎麼這麼吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你誤會了  大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…果然會招來惡運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  看到雛菊小姐的浴巾姿態不如說是幸運吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…這個  常識來講確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「確實是這樣」是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是說看到雛菊的裸體很興奮嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我可沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正雛菊小姐不體面的姿態在公寓的時候見得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒讓你看過那麼多次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是狼狽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:03:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  哈亞太他們也來拉斯維加斯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就在對面的賓館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雛菊小姐也因為坐飛機累了在那裡歇腳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真想見見他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  那我們就稍稍去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們三人是怎麼來拉斯維加斯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我們也是因為飛機出了點狀況就順便…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你們會在拉斯維加斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  稍微出了點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妹妹鶇被綁架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綁架？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  說成是綁架的話可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凪的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被綁架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…你們這是什麼登場方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  你們怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再這麼糾結這種細枝末節的小事我就要揍你了  哈亞太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而綁架卻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,頭等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我接CTU的Jack Bauer！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（CTU：美國反恐局，是電視連續劇《24》中被虛構出來的政府部門，\NJack Bauer則為片中主角）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  與其說是綁架…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說  像是惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  恐嚇信？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16}鶇琉璃就由我們看管了\N還想要她的命的話\N就記得來拉斯維加斯啊\N要用黑椿和鶇作交換哦\N\N9月24日晚上9點\N在如下地點見面!!\N不許報警!!\N\N拉斯維加斯郊外\N長有大樹的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什麼大事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的綁架啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去抓住壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  都說了不要做什麼多餘的舉動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快去阻止那群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們三個給我等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千櫻小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迦遊羅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾崎同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…為什麼你會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩位才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個  你看到我的眼鏡了嗎  眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  不要在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你再「啊」！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是做這種事的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點的話  那群笨蛋就真的去報警了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  為什麼你會在美國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在家享受生活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來話長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來話長？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們才是為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的賓館應該不是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過遇到了點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧住到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生情況了  快去找CTU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在快點幫我接CTU的Jack Bauer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？沒有這個組織也沒這號人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就找力也  快給我聯繫力也！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們給我適可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家給我聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次綁架不是鬧著玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}What has the black suit said?\N\N{\r}\N那個穿黑衣服的說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I understand Japanese a little.\N\N{\r}\N我懂一點日文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}He said, "I'm going to \Nkidnap someone seriously."\N\N{\r}\N\N\N他說「我現在是真的要綁架你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  快點把那封恐嚇信還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不嘛不嘛  好不容易拿到一封恐嚇信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}哈亞太的拜託什麼的才不聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}一不小心把它弄丟了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}"And there is a ransom note, which I wrote!"\N\N{\r}\N他說「那封恐嚇信是我寫的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Huh!?\N\N{\r}\N什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話只能來硬的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  快住手  就不給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}來硬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢啊  不要摸奇怪的地方啊  哈亞太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Freeze!\N\N{\r}\N不許動！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Hold up!\N\N{\r}\N舉起手來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你們誤會了  這是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Don't move!\N\N{\r}\N不要動！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它能把得到它的人的好運全部趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,招來不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}What are you thinking!\N\N{\r}\N你在想什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I'm scared!\N\N{\r}\N我好害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼吵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你幹了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要回恐嚇信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡把事情鬧大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇那邊就不是玩笑那麼簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之小颯你先離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這事想解決可有點麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Excuse me.\N\N{\r}\N打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Did you see the black suit guy \Nof the public indecency\N\N{\r}\N你們見到那個猥褻女性的穿黑衣服的人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}who had assaulted women around here?\N\N{\r}\N你們見到那個猥褻女性的穿黑衣服的人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猥褻？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I...I don't know.{\r}\N我…我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Thank you.{\r}\N謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是猥褻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你到底做了什麼啊  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是晚上8點半了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是真貨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  那個指針交匯在8的時候就有好運的說法也是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  綾崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…事到如今我也不會再吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  老師是由於什麼飛機事故才來這裡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是指望著在拉斯維加斯一夜暴富呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  為了可以隨時運錢我還借了車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是不錯  雖然是做白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你那懷錶是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這是只要拿著就會不幸的被詛咒的懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  為什麼特地帶著這種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據稱長針和短針交匯在8的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會有不得了的好事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那在那個時候投幣的話會不會中很多錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的可以就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也快到那個時候了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老師  這樣不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這下我就是億萬富姐了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  哈亞太那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}太好了太好了  我成了有錢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}一生不愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}一生都不用幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}明天就去辭職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…雪路她在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正肯定又在幹什麼不正經的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之明天買最好的車給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到託這塊錶的福可以贏到這麼多錢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這錶真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Hey.\N\N{\r}\N嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Give me everything you've got.\N\N{\r}\N把你所有的東西都給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…到底發生什麼事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那塊懷錶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和贏來的錢一起被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  因為我稍微不留意…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼就沒看緊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為…被桂老師拿去玩老虎機了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎機？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這事關鶇的性命  怎麼還有心情去玩老虎機啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…玩老虎機的並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管  快給我把黑椿找回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快到交易的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前一定要找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是鶇有什麼危險  那就是小颯你的錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛說得也太過火了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  快到交易的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯的過失我會承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承擔…是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交易就由我一個人去  想辦法解決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…小颯的事情就拜託瑪莉亞你幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯還真是辛苦啊  遇到這樣容易發火的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我們實在放心不下小凪你一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我們陪你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美國實在是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦啊  綾崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你問我怎麼辦也沒用啊  要是有點線索就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  哈亞太  雪路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  花菱小姐  朝風小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看見泉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  瀨川小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛想跟她開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻發現她人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  喂喂  是小雛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才躲在車尾  本來想從後面嚇一下小桂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知現在變得一團糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯  姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到交易地點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:14:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但看來是快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是朝這邊走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來就是那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是沙漠的中央嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇  你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到的話回答一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇  鶇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們帶著黑椿來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她…她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能把黑椿給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  黑椿被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被搶走了  所以我們沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被…搶走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在小颯正努力找回來  一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說被搶走了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你一兩句話解釋就行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志藤  鶇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也趕快去找黑椿去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你不是被綁架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛瑪莉亞小姐來電  說有黑椿的消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  地點在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  快把它找來給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  三千院凪就在我這裡當人質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來小凪是被那妖魔空間帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妖魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是普通的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…管她是妖魔也好不是也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能在我面前把小凪給帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓她後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  這下可糟了  伊澄她好久沒這樣認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  穿黑衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上聯絡警察  還有FBI  趕緊行動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泉  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不等警察到了再行動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  一下子就能把東西都奪回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也要確保泉沒事才行啊  別單獨行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可都是我的錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小步  警察還有多久才能到？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…貌似還有十分鐘左右才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Hey! We have to go before the cops get here!\N\N{\r}\N喂  我們得在警察到來之前離開這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  瀨川小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們有沒有拿著一塊錶呢  是塊懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個好像在一個身後紮著金髮的人的手上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身後紮著金髮的人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  鶇…鶇小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}We didn't have the time to \Nget away with the money?\N\N{\r}\N沒時間捲款逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}We went through a lot of \Ntrouble to steal it after all.\N\N{\r}\N難得搶到這麼一大筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下  鶇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的錢啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Shit! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危險  鶇小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯…？
